    <item>
      <title>美国前大使被捕，被控担任古巴特工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-03/urgent-former-us-ambassador-arrested-in-florida-accused-of-serving-as-an-agent-of-cuba-ap-source-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈阿密（美联社）——美联社获悉，一名曾担任美国驻玻利维亚大使的前美国外交官在联邦调查局长期反情报调查中被捕，他被指控秘密担任古巴政府特工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-03/urgent-former-us-ambassador-arrested-in-florida-accused-of-serving-as-an-agent-of-cuba-ap-source-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着就业危机的加剧，中国年轻人放弃城市梦想，转向乡村生活</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/china-youths-swap-city-dreams-for-country-living-as-jobs-crisis-mounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[龚成强曾在杭州的一家科技公司工作，年薪为 20 万元人民币（合 28,000 美元），但该公司在新冠疫情期间倒闭。他现在在浙江省农村种植草莓，在 40% 的收成因病害被毁后，预计损失至少相同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/china-youths-swap-city-dreams-for-country-living-as-jobs-crisis-mounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯称菲律宾爆炸案背后有外国恐怖分子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/foreign-terrorists-behind-deadly-philippine-bombing-marcos-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小费迪南德·马科斯总统表示，周日早些时候，菲律宾南部发生的爆炸事件是“外国恐怖分子制造的”，造成四人死亡、数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/foreign-terrorists-behind-deadly-philippine-bombing-marcos-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 15:13:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚马拉皮火山爆发，登山者受伤，村庄被火山灰覆盖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-03/urgent-indonesia-s-marapi-volcano-erupts-spewing-ash-plumes-and-blanketing-several-villages-with-ash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚巴东 (美联社) –印度尼西亚的马拉皮山周日喷发了白色和灰色的火山灰羽流，造成登山者搁浅和受伤，火山灰散布到几个村庄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-03/urgent-indonesia-s-marapi-volcano-erupts-spewing-ash-plumes-and-blanketing-several-villages-with-ash</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 11:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的政党赢得关键州民意调查，提高第三任期的竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/modi-set-to-win-key-state-polls-boosting-bid-to-stay-in-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度执政党印度人民党赢得了三场重要的州选举，并在其中两场选举中击败了反对派，加强了总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三次连任的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/modi-set-to-win-key-state-polls-boosting-bid-to-stay-in-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 11:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉与圭亚那石油争端激起民族主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-02/venezuela-stirs-nationalism-in-dispute-over-oil-rich-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几十年来，委内瑞拉的小学生一直被教导绘制一张与其他地方使用的不同的国家地图：他们的地图包括一个大约佛罗里达州大小的争议地区，由邻国圭亚那控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-02/venezuela-stirs-nationalism-in-dispute-over-oil-rich-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
